{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"339572-urusai-karasu","title":"うるさいカラス","description":"カー！カー！この本に登場するカラスは、子供たちにこの本を読んでほしいと呼びかけています。この本は「身近な動物」シリーズの4冊のうちの1冊です。","language":"Japanese","langCode":"ja","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Yoshihiro Nishimura"],"illustrators":["Deepa Balsavar"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/339572-urusai-karasu"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/704907/size3/13f658c3851393d29582f887eedc6f06.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/704907/size6/13f658c3851393d29582f887eedc6f06.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13204/size6/d17f80d3833c253f35e8faaeb955ceb0.jpg","text":"わたしはマンゴーのきにすんでるの。なつにはたくさんのじゅくしたフルーツをたべるんだよ。","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13205/size6/313fc3a7ffa1067458259ebcfb478d69.jpg","text":"こどもたちがすにいるときは、わたしがまもってやらないといけないの。","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13206/size6/bdb65056db20a0e7eab025a940266377.jpg","text":"わたしのすをのぞいていかない。わたしがみつけたすてきなたからものをみてちょうだい。","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13207/size6/ce503e57ae9d5dadf9cd00400617754e.jpg","text":"わたしはひこうきみたいにそらをとぶのがだいすきなの。","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13208/size6/637412987bf86d05b7d07f45fc75763c.jpg","text":"わたしはきにすわって、なにかおいしいものがないかさがすのよ。","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13209/size6/2d7497dd3aba1ba3abf5fd489d9d4613.jpg","text":"みぎをみて、ひだりをみて、、、","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13210/size6/7b26aa9ea72320f7588b7e2dd288a82e.jpg","text":"わたしはおさかながだいすき。おさかなをみつけると、とんでいってつかまえるの。","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13211/size6/1e5aa8dd2653515d570ba3b93863d653.jpg","text":"なきながら、ともだちをよんで、おさかなをいっしょにわけあうの。","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13212/size6/b3af99bbd1608c40e2af64c7c82a1644.jpg","text":"たまには、わたしに、『どっかいけ！うるさいとりめ』ってどなるひともいるわ。","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13213/size6/3d1aae61e53775597b12e1491b40510a.jpg","text":"きつねさんは、わたしのうたがすきなのよ。かれはじぶんでそういってたの。","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13214/size6/eb53d92756c6e3f5ba229f1c2f8cab7d.jpg","text":"あたらしいことばをおぼえよう\n﻿どうぶつやとりたちがだすおとには、","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13215/size6/2c62c3acf5e307aa581235f5aad391ba.jpg","text":"ライオンは『ガオー』\nいぬは『ワンワン』\nカラスはすごくなきごえがおおきいよ。だから、おおきなこえでしゃべるひとは、”カラスみたいにおおきいこえだね”っていわれるかもね。","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":15}}